== 分布范围 ==
[[File:Sarracenia_purpurea_PM.jpg|thumb]]
紫瓶子草分布于[[加拿大|加拿大]]与[[美国|美国]]。紫瓶子草在加拿大的分布范围从[[不列颠哥伦比亚省|不列颠哥伦比亚省]]东北部开始，至[[艾伯塔省|艾伯塔省]]、[[萨斯喀彻温省|萨斯喀彻温省]]、[[马尼托巴省|马尼托巴省]]、[[安大略|安大略]]及[[紐芬蘭與拉布拉多省|紐芬蘭與拉布拉多省]]南部（包括[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]与[[拉布拉多半岛|拉布拉多半岛]]南部）及其所有沿岸。在美国北部的分布范围包括[[新英格蘭|新英格蘭]]全部、[[五大湖|五大湖]]附近各州的全部或大部及[[爱荷华州|爱荷华州]]，[[西弗吉尼亚州|西弗吉尼亚州]]、[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]、[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]和[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]的部分。而在美国南部，其分布范围显著缩小，大部分分布于[[大西洋|大西洋]]沿岸及[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]东部沿岸，少量分布于[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]]西部[[阿巴拉契亚山脉|阿巴拉契亚山脉]]的高海拔地区及其附近。<ref name=PPA />

== 食虫性 ==
[[File:Wyeomyia_smithii_1.jpg|thumb]]
紫瓶子草與其他瓶子草屬物种一樣，會通過捕獲獵物來獲取養分。<ref>{{cite journal | author=Wakefield AE, Gotelli NJ, Wittman SE, Ellison AM | title=Prey addition alters nutrient stoichiometry of the carnivorous plant ''Sarracenia purpurea'' | journal=Ecology | volume=86 | year=2005 | pages=1737–1743 | url=http://www.esajournals.org/esaonline/?request=get-abstract&issn=0012-9658&volume=086&issue=07&page=1737 | doi=10.1890/04-1673 | format=abstract | issue=7}}</ref>但其捕獲的效率是非常低下的，在所有到訪捕蟲瓶的昆蟲中只有不到1%的獵物會掉進瓶子裡。<ref>{{cite journal | author=Newell SJ, Nastase AJ | title=Efficiency of nutrient capture by ''Sarracenia purpurea'' (Sarraceniaceae), the Northern Pitcher Plant | journal=American Journal of Botany | volume=85 | year=1998 | pages=88–91 | doi=10.2307/2446558 | issue=1 | jstor=2446558}}</ref>即使如此，栽培者卻常觀察到，在溫暖的夏季，捕蟲瓶很快就能捕獲許多獵物。[[蒼蠅|蒼蠅]]、[[蚊子|蚊子]]、[[螞蟻|螞蟻]]、[[蜘蛛|蜘蛛]]、甚至於[[蛾|蛾類]]等獵物落入瓶中，會被瓶底累積的雨水淹死。接著捕蟲瓶內的[[無脊椎動物|無脊椎動物]]群落將把這些獵物遺骸分解。紫瓶子草內的群集主要由[[史密斯瓶子草蚊|史密斯瓶子草蚊]]{{small|（''Wyeomyia smithii''）}}和一種[[中足摇蚊|中足摇蚊]]{{small|（''Metriocnemus knabi''）}}組成。它們與紫瓶子草之間存在著共生關係。<ref>C. Michael Hogan. 2011. [http://www.eoearth.org/article/Commensalism?topic=58074 ''Commensalism''. Topic Ed. M.Mcginley. Ed-in-chief C.J.Cleveland. Encyclopedia of Earth. National Council for Science and the Environment. Washington DC] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eoearth.org/article/Commensalism?topic=58074 |date=20130526140316 }}</ref>

此外，[[原生生物|原生生物]]、[[輪蟲|輪蟲]]及細菌，形成了底層的[[食物網|食物網]]，將獵物殘骸破碎、無機化，變成植物能吸收的養分。<ref>{{cite journal | author=Heard SB | title=Pitcher plant midges and mosquitoes: a processing chain commensalism | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_ecology_1994-09_75_6/page/1647 | journal=Ecology | volume=75 | year=1994 | pages=1647–1660 | doi=10.2307/1939625 | format=abstract | issue=6 | jstor=1939625}}</ref><ref name="Mouquet 2008">{{cite journal | author = Mouquet N., Daufresne T., Gray S. M., Miller T. E. | year = 2008 | title = Modelling the relationship between a pitcher plant (''Sarracenia purpurea'') and its phytotelma community: mutualism or parasitism? | url = | journal = Functional Ecology | volume = 22 | issue = 4| pages = 728–737 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2435.2008.01421.x }}</ref><ref name="Peterson 2008">{{cite journal | author = Peterson C. N., Day S., Wolfe B. E., Ellison A. M., Kolter R., Pringle A. | year = 2008 | title = A keystone predator controls bacterial diversity in the pitcher-plant (''Sarracenia purpurea'') microecosystem | url = | journal = Environmental Microbiology | volume = 10 | issue = 9| pages = 2257–2266 | doi = 10.1111/j.1462-2920.2008.01648.x | pmid = 18479443 }}</ref>紫瓶子草新生葉片可產生[[消化酶|消化酶]]，如[[水解酶|水解酶]]及[[蛋白酶|蛋白酶]]，少數葉片在成熟後的第二年仍能產酶。捕蟲瓶內細菌群落的活動僅為紫瓶子草消化獵物遺骸的輔助方式。<ref name="Rice 2007">Rice, Barry. (2007). [http://www.sarracenia.com/faq/faq5538.html About ''Sarracenia purpurea'', the purple pitcher plant] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sarracenia.com/faq/faq5538.html |date=20210406112247 }}. The Carnivorous Plant FAQ. Accessed online: 21 June 2008.</ref><ref name="Gallie and Chang 1997">{{cite journal | author = Gallie D. R., Chang S.-C. | year = 1997 | title = Signal transduction in the carnivorous plant Sarracenia purpurea. Regulation of secretory hydrolase expression during development and in response to resources | url = http://www.plantphysiol.org/cgi/reprint/115/4/1461 | journal = Plant Physiology | volume = 115 | issue = 4 | pages = 1461–1471 | pmid = 9414556 | doi = 10.1104/pp.115.4.1461 | pmc = 158611 | access-date = 2012-03-14 | archive-date = 2005-02-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20050213220120/http://www.plantphysiol.org/cgi/reprint/115/4/1461 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

